reviews.review_text: First Show Thank you for uploading this show. This has special meaning for me as it was the first GD show that I ever attended. I have been hooked since!! This is the first time U have heard it in over 18yrs, and thats how old I was when I went...Jeez time flies! This period obviously isnt one of their best by all means, but none the less its the GD. A lot of Jems I got to witness on the first night with a couple Dylan songs thrown in for good measure! An unbelievable concert...just wish I remebered it more LOL!!! AUD quality is nice in the cans, have yet to put it on stereo, but from what I have heard (and I am a professional, engineer that is) it will sound lovely..and I cant wait to turn it up!!! Thanks again for the upload Andrew!!! GOD Bless the GD.....5 stars for Personal reasons stated above
